description: I don't know about you, but I love a good transformation story. This week's guest, Jess Guilbeaux, is a perfect example of that. She was a former guest (season 3, episode 5) on the insanely popular Netflix show Queer Eye with the Fab Five and will share her emotional transformation journey, the lessons she's learned, and what she's doing now.
